data.description: Discover the perfect harmony of luxury, comfort, and outdoor living in this distinguished two-story home nestled in the Manchester Crossing subdivision and located in one of the top-rated school districts.  This home seamlessly combines classic architecture with modern comforts, offering a perfect blend of style and functionality.  The home’s exterior, adorned with a classic brick and stone is a timeless elegance.  You are welcomed in with beautiful wood floors and a grand foyer that creates an open and airy ambiance, enhancing the charm of the home.  As you make your way into the home, you’ll be captivated by a majestic stone fireplace.  The open layout seamlessly connects the living room to the kitchen fostering a sense of togetherness.  The kitchen is a culinary haven with modern appliances, granite countertops, a walk-in pantry, and a layout designed for both practicality and aesthetic appeal.  Retreat to the primary suite that offers vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, double vanity, and a soaker tub with a walk-in shower.  A second bedroom with an ensuite bathroom is perfect for guests.  Two more generously sized bedrooms with a Jack and Jill style bathroom that leads to a bonus room which is perfect for a fourth bedroom or a family room. Descend into the impressive, finished basement, providing additional living space that can be customized to suit various needs. The finished basement opens to a walk out patio connecting indoor and outdoor living.   Start envisioning a lifestyle filled with comfort, relaxation, and the beauty of this charming home! Updates: Some New Carpet, Furnace (2023), Central Air (2023), Water Softener (2020), Water Heater (2019), Washer & Dryer (3-5 years), New Well Pump.
